-- Portugal Finance Minister Teixeira to Meet Chinese Counterpart, Lusa Says
-- B y   J o a o   L i m a
-- 2010-12-12T11:46:56Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-12/portugal-s-santos-to-meet-china-s-finance-minister-lusa-reports.html
Portuguese Finance Minister  Fernando Teixeira dos Santos  will meet Chinese Finance Minister Xie Xuren
and Chinese central bank Governor Zhou Xiaochuan in Beijing on
Dec. 13, Lusa reported, without saying how it obtained the
information.  The meetings are related to China’s availability to buy
Portuguese debt, demonstrated during Chinese President  Hu Jintao ’s visit to Portugal about a month ago, the Portuguese
news agency said.  Teixeira dos Santos arrived in Beijing today with Carlos
Costa Pina, Portugal’s secretary of state for treasury and
finance, and  Alberto Soares , president of Portugal’s government
debt agency, according to Lusa.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Joao Lima at 
 jlima1@bloomberg.net  